    "We sample 1,000 evaluation examples for all tasks with larger data sizes, and additionally sample 32 held-out examples for computing the bias score metric (§2.3), and 64 more examples to use as a pool of instances for choosing in-context demonstrations and LoRA fine-tuning examples.",
    "We only include tasks with at least 300 evaluation examples in our experiments.",
    "For details on the selected tasks, see App.",
    "We experiment with models of different sizes from three LLM families: Llama-2 7B and 13B (Touvron et al., 2023), Mistral 7B (Jiang et al., 2023a), and Falcon 7B and 40B (Penedo et al., 2023).",
    "We use both the base and instruction fine-tuned versions of each model."
